        Parameters:
        colVarIds - Collection of variety IDs
        sChr - Contig name
        lStart - Start bp position
        lEnd - End bp position
        bSNP - Query SNPs
        bIndel - Query INDELs
        bCoreonly - Use core SNPs omly
        bMismatchonly - Include only varieties with mismatch in region
        poslist - Position list
        sSubpopulation - Query only subpopulation
        sLocus - Query within locus
        bAlignIndels - Display INDels as multiple sequence alignment
        bShowAllRefAlleles - Show alleles for all reference genomes
